org.memoize.group19

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.memoize.group19.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a user and contains all fields and methods necessary for a user to add a reminder, a subscription or a group.
    Author:
    group 19
